{"tid":113960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"曾涉不良銷售　M Boxing Fitness突停業","createTime":"2017-02-09T11:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T17:47:42.000Z","uid":43033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1b83bf1576da5a643567cd19f31de9b21b6226","tid":113960,"uid":43033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:44:10.000Z","msg":"曾經上去試玩， 差d就中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上月爆出有健身教練涉以賤招劏客的健身中心M Boxing Fitness今(8日)突然停業，至少有300名市民受影響。多名受影響客人今傍晚到該健身中心了解，其中，去年以3萬港元購買健身服務的事主慨嘆成為「豬仔」，當時未有用信用卡過數，而是應中心要求以網上支付工具過數，至今追討無門；另有事主稱剛在農曆新年期間以4000多港元購買健身課程，未料享用1堂即遇上結業，大嘆流年不利；另有大學生以8港元一堂的「學生價」報堂試玩，未料同樣中招。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170208/mobile/bkn-20170208173111696-0208_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170208%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170208173111696-0208_00822_001.html&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2y7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=9c55ad60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170208/mobile/bkn-20170208173111696-0208_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n係度告誡各位 唔咁輕易簽約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l9esuaj5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl9esuaj5&h=676ab96f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2db73437d96ae4ec5bae52b3b6ffa3fab0c8f20f","tid":113960,"uid":15206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:12:35.000Z","msg":"想問你點樣整張咁長既Whatsapp screen cap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8db39c06ead48b11e26fca5a2792f3965787e2","tid":113960,"uid":30487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"健身狗<br />\n地產狗<br />\n保險狗<b